---
import BaseLayout from '../components/layout/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Use — BKK Songkran" description="Terms of use for BKK Songkran.com, the Songkran 2026 Bangkok festival guide." canonical="https://bkksongkran.com/terms">

  <section class="pt-36 pb-24 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">

      <div class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-3" style="color:#006479;">Legal</div>
      <h1 class="font-headline font-extrabold tracking-tighter mb-2" style="font-size:clamp(2.5rem,6vw,4rem);color:#003345;line-height:0.95;">Terms of Use</h1>
      <p class="text-sm mb-12" style="color:#6b8fa3;">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-10 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color:#326177;">

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-lg mb-3" style="color:#003345;">Acceptance</h2>
          <p>By accessing or using BKK Songkran.com ("the Site"), you agree to these Terms of Use. If you do not agree, please do not use the Site. We reserve the right to update these terms at any time; continued use constitutes acceptance.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-lg mb-3" style="color:#003345;">What BKK Songkran is</h2>
          <p>BKK Songkran is an <strong>independent, fan-run information guide</strong> for Songkran 2026 in Bangkok. We are not affiliated with, endorsed by, or acting as an agent for any festival organiser, venue, ticketing company, hotel, transport operator, or the Thai government. We do not sell tickets or book accommodation.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-lg mb-3" style="color:#003345;">Accuracy of information</h2>
          <p>We make every effort to keep event information, lineups, dates, venues, and transport details accurate. However:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 list-disc list-inside mt-2">
            <li>Lineups, dates, and venues can change without notice — always verify with official festival sources before purchasing tickets or making travel arrangements</li>
            <li>Road closure and transport information is based on historical patterns and announced plans — confirm with Thai authorities closer to the dates</li>
            <li>The AI guide (Nong) provides general information and may occasionally be inaccurate — do not rely on it as a sole source for safety-critical decisions</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-lg mb-3" style="color:#003345;">User conduct</h2>
          <p>You agree not to:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 list-disc list-inside mt-2">
            <li>Use the Site for unlawful purposes</li>
            <li>Attempt to scrape, copy, or republish content without permission</li>
            <li>Use the AI guide to generate harmful, deceptive, or illegal content</li>
            <li>Interfere with or disrupt the Site's infrastructure</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-lg mb-3" style="color:#003345;">Intellectual property</h2>
          <p>All original content on BKK Songkran — including text, design, graphics, and code — is owned by BKK Songkran. Festival names, artist names, and event branding are property of their respective owners and are referenced for informational purposes only under fair use. If you are a rights holder with a concern, contact <a href="mailto:hello@bkksongkran.com" class="underline" style="color:#006479;">hello@bkksongkran.com</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-lg mb-3" style="color:#003345;">Limitation of liability</h2>
          <p>To the maximum extent permitted by law, BKK Songkran and its operators shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 list-disc list-inside mt-2">
            <li>Reliance on information published on the Site</li>
            <li>Decisions made based on AI guide responses</li>
            <li>Festival cancellations, lineup changes, or venue closures</li>
            <li>Personal injury, loss, or theft during the festival</li>
            <li>Disruption to transport or road access during Songkran</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">Use of the Site is entirely at your own risk.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-lg mb-3" style="color:#003345;">External links</h2>
          <p>The Site contains links to third-party websites (festival organisers, ticketing platforms, etc.). We have no control over those sites and are not responsible for their content or practices.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-lg mb-3" style="color:#003345;">Governing law</h2>
          <p>These terms are governed by the laws of Thailand. Any disputes shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of Thai courts.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-lg mb-3" style="color:#003345;">Contact</h2>
          <p><a href="mailto:hello@bkksongkran.com" class="underline hover:text-primary" style="color:#006479;">hello@bkksongkran.com</a></p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
